OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776942175
OL,3,CEvacuations and 100m cordon after
OL,4,Ccentury-old chemicals found
OL,6,FA 100m cordon was set up and homes and
OL,7,Fbusinesses evacuated after hazardous
OL,8,Fchemicals were found among heritage
OL,9,Fitems at a photography studio.
OL,11,FBosses at W.W. Winter Ltd, which has
OL,12,Fbeen based in Midland Road in Derby
OL,13,Fsince 1867, said the items were more
OL,14,Fthan 100 years old.
OL,16,FThey called the police on Tuesday 21
OL,17,FApril who took the items to a secure
OL,18,Farea in Elvaston Castle Country Park,
OL,19,Fwhere a controlled explosion was
OL,20,Fcarried out.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
