CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776942175
OL,3,CEvacuations and 100m cordon after
OL,4,Ccentury-old chemicals found
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the business said:
OL,7,F"The police incident on Midland Road
OL,8,Ftoday was the result of W. W. Winter
OL,9,FLtd discovering 100+ year old
OL,10,Fchemicals amongst their heritage
OL,11,Fitems, which, after some research,
OL,12,Fgave cause for concern, due to their
OL,13,Fvolatile nature.
OL,15,F"We contacted the police to find out
OL,16,Fthe correct means of disposal and were
OL,17,Fadvised the chemicals were a serious
OL,18,Frisk to public safety.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776942175
OL,3,CEvacuations and 100m cordon after
OL,4,Ccentury-old chemicals found
OL,6,F"As a result, the police contacted the
OL,7,Fbomb squad, who removed the item for a
OL,8,Fcontrolled explosion.
OL,10,F"A cordon of 100 metres was put in
OL,11,Fplace during this procedure."
OL,13,FW.W. Winter Ltd confirmed on Facebook
OL,14,Fthat the chemical was picric acid,
OL,15,Fdiscovered among their historical
OL,16,Fitems.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776942175
OL,3,CEvacuations and 100m cordon after
OL,4,Ccentury-old chemicals found
OL,6,F"On this occasion the picric acid
OL,7,Fraised concern. We contacted the
OL,8,Fappropriate authorities, who then
OL,9,Fcalled in the bomb squad for a
OL,10,Fcontrolled explosion."
OL,12,FLeader of Derby City Council, Nadine
OL,13,FPeatfield, shared W.W. Winter's
OL,14,Fstatement, adding: "Everything has
OL,15,Fbeen made safe and the road is open
OL,16,Fagain. Glad that everyone at WW Winter
OL,17,Fis safe, I was only there last week."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776942175
OL,3,CEvacuations and 100m cordon after
OL,4,Ccentury-old chemicals found
OL,6,FSeven roads including London Road and
OL,7,FMidland Road, as well as Litchurch
OL,8,FStreet, Wellington Street, Regent
OL,9,FStreet, Nelson Street, Oxford Street
OL,10,Fand Carrington Street were closed and
OL,11,Fhomes and businesses evacuated as a
OL,12,Fprecaution.
OL,14,FDerbyshire police shared an update at
OL,15,F4.20pm, nearly six hours after they
OL,16,Ffirst received a call, confirming the
OL,17,Fhazardous chemicals had been removed
OL,18,Ffrom the scene and destroyed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
