OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776942175
OL,3,CEvacuations and 100m cordon after
OL,4,Ccentury-old chemicals found
OL,6,F"The Army's Explosives Ordnance
OL,7,FDisposal unit, supported by a police
OL,8,Fescort, transported the substances to
OL,9,Fa secured area within Elvaston Castle
OL,10,FCountry Park where a controlled
OL,11,Fexplosion on the chemicals was
OL,12,Fcommenced," a spokesperson for the
OL,13,Fforce added.
OL,15,F"Members of the public who were close-
OL,16,Fby may have heard a loud bang but we
OL,17,Fwould like to reassure everyone that
OL,18,Fthere is no reason to be alarmed."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
